TITLE: Poly1305 Example Usage in V
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates the usage of the Poly1305 MAC implementation in V. It decodes a hexadecimal key, defines a message, generates a Poly1305 tag for the message using the key, and then verifies the generated tag. The example relies on the `encoding.hex` and `x.crypto.poly1305` modules.
